        <article><![CDATA[<p>Brainboard creates Architecture Templates as Record Producers in ServiceNow.<br />To allow the app to create Record Producers, you need to allow the table to perform Create/Read/Write/Delete operations from other application scopes.</p>
<ol style="list-style-position: inside;"><li>Click &#34;Configure&#34; button, then go to the Application Access tab.</li><li>Set Accessible from to All application scopes.</li><li>Check the following options:
